    "1, 111102:8 Requirements analysisThe purpose of requirements analysis is to systematically identify, understand, and document the software requirements for a given system or software project.Li et al. [49] proposed a new technique named RENE, which uses the LSTM-CRF model for requirements entity extraction and introduces general knowledge to reduce the need for labeled data.",
